usage: loto lock <target> [<target>...] -t "why"

Acquire a lock on one or more targets. -t (intent) is required.

examples:
  loto lock internal/store/store.go -t "store refactor"
  loto lock a.go b.go -t "rename sweep"
  -intent string
    	intent (required)
  -t string
    	intent (required)
  -ttl duration
    	lock TTL (default 30m0s)
